    // If u1 in U, u2 in U, and u1 % u2 == 0, then u1 can become u2.
    // This forms a directed graph where an edge exists from u1 to u2 if u1 % u2 == 0.
    // We want to find, for each initial number nums[i], the minimum value reachable from nums[i]
